P2 Badge Clear stale live-region text when a refresh fails

On failure, the code cancels the pending clear timer but does not clear the existing "Dashboard updated" text, so a failure that occurs within the 1s window after a prior success can leave a stale success message in the live region indefinitely. This can mislead assistive-tech users and can also suppress a later success announcement when the same text is written again.

